    <header id="main_text" class="text-center col-md-12" >
      <strong><h1> Waiting in line sucks. Let us do it for you.</h1></strong>
      <button class="btn btn-success" ng-click="">Learn more</button>
    </header>
  </div>    
  <div class="row jumbotron ">
    
    <article class="col-md-5">
      <h2>User Signup</h2>
      <p>Instead of standing in line all day, wouldn't you rather have a cup of coffee?</p>
